OL,3,GOPINIONCFinal curtain for Grampian TV
OL,4,Cas Ofcom backs STV changes
OL,5,
OL,6,FSo, as expected, Ofcom is to allow big
OL,7,Fchanges to STV News.
OL,9,FThere was an inevitability about this,
OL,10,Fdespite huge opposition in the north of
OL,11,FScotland.
OL,13,FAnd no wonder there was concern.
OL,15,FThis represents the end of the old
OL,16,FGrampian TV region in every meaningful
OL,17,Fsense. The only bespoke output for the
OL,18,Fnorth will be presented from a studio
OL,19,Fin Glasgow.
OL,23,EPub: 02-Jun-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,144,140,200,120,0,100
