PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F143A1781467885
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCFinal curtain for Grampian TV
OL,4,Cas Ofcom backs STV changes
OL,5,
OL,6,FViewers in the Central Belt will lose
OL,7,Fsub-opts and see some of the bigger
OL,8,Fstories from the north but won't notice
OL,9,Fsuch fundamental changes.
OL,11,FWe know the headlines about the new
OL,12,Fservice.
OL,14,F- All studio presentation will come
OL,15,Ffrom Glasgow.
OL,17,F- All news output will be shared
OL,18,Fbetween both STV Central and STV North
OL,19,Fexcept for 30pc of the 6pm programme.
OL,21,FThe changes will take place over the
OL,22,Fsummer. No dates have been announced.
OL,23,EPub: 02-Jun-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,144,140,200,120,0,100
